reviews.review_text: Damn fine AUD It sounds like tape speed may be an issue in first few songs, perhaps the boys were just amped up as Nassau tended to have that effect.  Anyway, I have Go to Nassau and while not having done a close 'side by side' I can say that this recording definitely does it for me. Second set is really something - great representation of 80
The Dew nice second set to end a good tour
